{"tha-ap11:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap11:0.2":"Buddhavagga ","tha-ap11:0.3":"Khadiravaniyarevatattheraapadana ","tha-ap11:1.1":"“Ganga bhagirathi nama, ","tha-ap11:1.2":"himavanta pabhavita; ","tha-ap11:1.3":"Kutitthe naviko asim, ","tha-ap11:1.4":"orime ca tarim aham. ","tha-ap11:2.1":"Padumuttaro nayako, ","tha-ap11:2.2":"sambuddho dvipaduttamo; ","tha-ap11:2.3":"Vasi satasahassehi, ","tha-ap11:2.4":"gangatiramupagato. ","tha-ap11:3.1":"Bahu nava samanetva, ","tha-ap11:3.2":"vaddhakihi susankhatam; ","tha-ap11:3.3":"Navaya chadanam katva, ","tha-ap11:3.4":"patimanim narasabham. ","tha-ap11:4.1":"Agantvana ca sambuddho, ","tha-ap11:4.2":"aruhi tanca navakam; ","tha-ap11:4.3":"Varimajjhe thito sattha, ","tha-ap11:4.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap11:5.1":"‘Yo so taresi sambuddham, ","tha-ap11:5.2":"sanghancapi anasavam; ","tha-ap11:5.3":"Tena cittappasadena, ","tha-ap11:5.4":"devaloke ramissati. ","tha-ap11:6.1":"Nibbattissati te byamham, ","tha-ap11:6.2":"sukatam navasanthitam; ","tha-ap11:6.3":"Akase pupphachadanam, ","tha-ap11:6.4":"dharayissati sabbada. ","tha-ap11:7.1":"Atthapannasakappamhi, ","tha-ap11:7.2":"tarako nama khattiyo; ","tha-ap11:7.3":"Caturanto vijitavi, ","tha-ap11:7.4":"cakkavatti bhavissati. ","tha-ap11:8.1":"Sattapannasakappamhi, ","tha-ap11:8.2":"cammako nama khattiyo; ","tha-ap11:8.3":"Uggacchantova suriyo, ","tha-ap11:8.4":"jotissati mahabbalo. ","tha-ap11:9.1":"Kappasatasahassamhi, ","tha-ap11:9.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap11:9.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap11:9.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap11:10.1":"Tidasa so cavitvana, ","tha-ap11:10.2":"manussattam gamissati; ","tha-ap11:10.3":"Revato nama namena, ","tha-ap11:10.4":"brahmabandhu bhavissati. ","tha-ap11:11.1":"Agara nikkhamitvana, ","tha-ap11:11.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap11:11.3":"Gotamassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap11:11.4":"sasane pabbajissati. ","tha-ap11:12.1":"So paccha pabbajitvana, ","tha-ap11:12.2":"yuttayogo vipassako; ","tha-ap11:12.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap11:12.4":"nibbayissatinasavo’. ","tha-ap11:13.1":"Viriyam me dhuradhorayham, ","tha-ap11:13.2":"Yogakkhemadhivahanam; ","tha-ap11:13.3":"Dharemi antimam deham, ","tha-ap11:13.4":"Sammasambuddhasasane. ","tha-ap11:14.1":"Satasahasse katam kammam, ","tha-ap11:14.2":"phalam dassesi me idha; ","tha-ap11:14.3":"Sumutto saravegova, ","tha-ap11:14.4":"kilese jhapayi mama. ","tha-ap11:15.1":"Tato mam vananiratam, ","tha-ap11:15.2":"disva lokantagu muni; ","tha-ap11:15.3":"Vanavasibhikkhunaggam, ","tha-ap11:15.4":"pannapesi mahamati. ","tha-ap11:16.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap11:16.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap11:16.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap11:16.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap11:17.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma khadiravaniyo revato thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap11:18.1":"Khadiravaniyarevatattherassapadanam navamam. "}